import MasterPage from "./pages/MasterPage"
import DevelopmentPage from "./pages/DevelopmentPage"
import ReleasePage from "./pages/ReleasePage"

import shketDev from "./assets/shket-dev.png"
import broekFork from "./assets/broken_fork_logo.png"
import unknownPng from "./assets/unknown.png"

export const MASTER_PATH = "/master"
export const DEVELOPMENT_PATH = "/development"
export const RELEASE_PATH = "/release"

export const routes = [
  {path: MASTER_PATH, Component: MasterPage, title: "master"},
  {path: DEVELOPMENT_PATH, Component: DevelopmentPage, title: "development"},
  {path: RELEASE_PATH, Component: ReleasePage, title: "release"},
]

export const slides = [
  {name: "shket-dev", image: shketDev, description: "My epic website"},
  {name: "Broken Fork", image: broekFork, description: "Describe everything using only fork!"},
  {name: "unknown", image: unknownPng, description: null},
]
